; Regression test for issue #865: uncleared posts are no longer bold when used in combination with '--payee note' option. (BZ#865)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/865
;
; Without --payee note, uncleared transactions are shown in bold (ESC[1m).
; With --payee note, the bold code is missing (bug).

2024/01/01 Payee
    ; note: This is a note
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; Baseline: without --payee note, uncleared payee is bold
test reg --force-color
24-Jan-01 [1mPayee                [0m [34mExpenses:Food         [0m       $10.00       $10.00
                                [34mAssets:Cash           [0m      [31m$-10.00[0m            0
end test

; Bug: with --payee note, uncleared transaction loses bold formatting
test reg --force-color --payee note
24-Jan-01  note: This is a note [34mExpenses:Food         [0m       $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-01  note: This is a note [34mAssets:Cash           [0m      [31m$-10.00[0m            0
end test
